oe14-skill-tree-blaksmithing-name = Blacksmithing
oe14-skill-tree-blaksmithing-desc = Explore and create new items from metal.

oe14-skill-tree-pyrokinetic-name = Pyrokinesis
oe14-skill-tree-pyrokinetic-desc = Master the magic of fire, allowing you to warm, illuminate, and destroy.

oe14-skill-tree-hydrosophistry-name = Hydrosophy
oe14-skill-tree-hydrosophistry-desc = Master the magic of water and frost to create items from water and ice, and freeze enemies.

oe14-skill-tree-metamagic-name = Metamagic
oe14-skill-tree-metamagic-desc = Explore ways to subtly manipulate magic to affect spells and items.

oe14-skill-tree-illusion-name = Illusion
oe14-skill-tree-illusion-desc = Explore the nature of light to create illusions, light sources and shadows.

oe14-skill-tree-healing-name = Vivification
oe14-skill-tree-healing-desc = Explore the ways in which magic affects living creatures.

oe14-skill-tree-dimension-name = Dimensionomy
oe14-skill-tree-dimension-desc = Immerse yourself in the nature of space and void.

oe14-skill-tree-electric-name = Electromancy
oe14-skill-tree-electric-desc = Discover the nature of deafening storms, winds, and thunderstorms.

