oe14-skill-tree-athletic-name = Athletic
oe14-skill-tree-athletic-desc = Develop your body by pushing the boundaries of what is available.

oe14-skill-tree-martial-name = Martial arts
oe14-skill-tree-martial-desc = Master the secrets of deadly weapons, or make your own body a weapon.

